OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783680590
OL,3,CLobular breast cancer campaigner urges
OL,4,CAndy Burnham to back 'moon shot'
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FThe widower of a breast cancer
OL,8,Fcampaigner from Sussex has urged Andy
OL,9,FBurnham to show 'leadership' and
OL,10,Fcommit to fund 'vital' research into
OL,11,Fthe second most common type of the
OL,12,Fdisease.
OL,14,FDr Susan Michaelis died in 2025, 14
OL,15,Fyears after being diagnosed with
OL,16,Flobular breast cancer, for which there
OL,17,Fare no specific treatments.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
