OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783680590
OL,3,CLobular breast cancer campaigner urges
OL,4,CAndy Burnham to back 'moon shot'
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FIn the final two years of her life,
OL,8,Fshe had led a campaign to raise #20
OL,9,Fmillion for a five-year research study
OL,10,Fto understand the basic biology of the
OL,11,Finvasive form of cancer.
OL,13,FHer husband, Tristan Loraine, has
OL,14,Fappealed directly to the likely next
OL,15,Fprime minister to back the Lobular
OL,16,FMoon Shot Project.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783680590
OL,3,CLobular breast cancer campaigner urges
OL,4,CAndy Burnham to back 'moon shot'
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV News Meridian on the
OL,8,Ffirst anniversary of his wife's death,
OL,9,FMr Loraine said: "Last year on 30
OL,10,FJune, nine days before my wife died,
OL,11,Fshe went to Manchester on emergency
OL,12,Foxygen to meet the scientists who are
OL,13,Fgoing to lead the research.
OL,15,F"Andy Burnham was meant to chair that
OL,16,Fmeeting but he had covid. However he
OL,17,Fissued a statement saying that he
OL,18,Ffully supported the project as a
OL,19,Fformer health secretary.
OL,26,@qD@ROUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783680590
OL,3,CLobular breast cancer campaigner urges
OL,4,CAndy Burnham to back 'moon shot'
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,F"Unfortunately Keir Starmer didn't
OL,8,Fhave the leadership to listen...
OL,9,Fhopefully Andy Burnham will when he
OL,10,Fbecomes prime minister."
OL,12,FA memorial debate in honour of Dr
OL,13,FSusan Michaelis was held in
OL,14,FParliament's Westminster Hall on 9
OL,15,FJuly by her local MP John Milne.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783680590
OL,3,CLobular breast cancer campaigner urges
OL,4,CAndy Burnham to back 'moon shot'
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FMr Milne, who represents Horsham in
OL,8,FWest Sussex, described Dr Michaelis as
OL,9,Fan "inspiration" and said he
OL,10,F"staggered and shocked" to discover
OL,11,Fthere were no specific treatments for
OL,12,Flobular breast cancer.
OL,14,FThe spokesperson for the Department of
OL,15,FHealth and Social Care said: "Our
OL,16,Fsympathies go out to women and
OL,17,Ffamilies impacted by lobular breast
OL,18,Fcancer.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783680590
OL,3,CLobular breast cancer campaigner urges
OL,4,CAndy Burnham to back 'moon shot'
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,F"This form of cancer sadly goes
OL,8,Fundetected in too many women, and we
OL,9,Fare determined to back research that
OL,10,Fcould transform outcomes for patients.
OL,12,F"Lord (Patrick) Vallance and Minister
OL,13,F(Sharon) Hodgson met with the Lobular
OL,14,FMoon Shot Project about how best to
OL,15,Fprogress research in this vital area.
OL,26,@tD@GpmtD@OpnuD@ApmuD@Hpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783680590
OL,3,CLobular breast cancer campaigner urges
OL,4,CAndy Burnham to back 'moon shot'
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,F"We know there is more we can do and
OL,8,Four National Cancer Plan is putting
OL,9,Fresearch at the heart of improving
OL,10,Foutcomes, helping to bring the latest
OL,11,Fscientific breakthroughs into the NHS
OL,12,Ffaster so that patients benefit from
OL,13,Fearlier diagnosis, more effective
OL,14,Ftreatments, and better quality of
OL,15,Flife."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
