PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1783680590
OL,3,CLobular breast cancer campaigner urges
OL,4,CAndy Burnham to back 'moon shot'
OL,5,Cresearch
OL,7,FA statement issued by Andy Burnham
OL,8,Ffrom June 2025, when he was mayor of
OL,9,FGreater Manchester, said he was "proud
OL,10,Fto back the Lobular Moon Shot
OL,11,FProject", adding that "thousands of
OL,12,Fwomen in this country" still don't
OL,13,F"have the dedicated treatments" they
OL,14,Fneed.
OL,26,@qD@aOUsD@HO]sD@WOUtD@VO]uD@AOUuD@_O]
